<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4900771>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 28. Comparison of the pelvis of: A - Patagornis marshi (BMNH-A516) and B - Andalgalornis steulleti (FM-P14357). The joined dorsal iliac crests form a dorsal projection on the most cranial part in Patagornis (A), whilst in Andalgalornis (B) this projection does not exist and the crest is higher in half of the pelvis." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4900771/files/figure.png" .

